---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/molecules/Hero.astro';
import Button from '../components/atoms/Button.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="CSR" description="Aviaco France CSR commitment - B Corp Certification, waste sorting, recycling, and environmental impact reduction">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <Hero 
    title="CSR" 
    image="/copter/9.jpg"
    imageAlt="Corporate Social Responsibility"
  />

  <!-- Introduction Section -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <p class="font-outfit text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Aviaco France strengthens its commitment to CSR. Fully involved in its social responsibilities as a company, Aviaco increases its actions to reinforce its positive impact in terms of human resources, environment, and society.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sorting and Recycling Section -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl mb-5 md:mb-6 lg:mb-8 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              Sorting and recycling
            </h2>
            <p class="font-outfit text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Since 2021, Aviaco France works with Lemontri, a local company, to sort its waste. Special bins for office waste (paper, cardboard…) and food waste (cans, plastic bottles…) have been installed.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-8 md:mt-0">
            <div class="aspect-square w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl shadow-xl">
              <img 
                src="/copter/10.jpg" 
                alt="Sorting and recycling" 
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- B Corp Section -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl mb-5 md:mb-6 lg:mb-8 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
          Certified B Corporation™
        </h2>
        <p class="font-outfit text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-5 md:mb-6">
          Aviaco France has earned B Corp Certification in May 2024 from the non-profit B Lab. Being a member of the Certified B Corporation™ community requires a holistic review of a business' social and environmental performance, accountability and transparency, and is based on a vision of creating a community of for-profit companies committed to redefining success in business.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Image Section -->
  <section class="py-8 md:py-10 lg:py-12 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="aspect-square w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl shadow-2xl">
          <img 
            src="/copter/11.jpg" 
            alt="B Corp Certification" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Impact Section -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl mb-5 md:mb-6 lg:mb-8 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
          Thanks to sorting, we have saved
        </h2>
        <p class="font-outfit text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-5 md:mb-6">
          In our efforts, we have managed to reduce more than 277 kilograms of waste and cut down over 48 kilograms of CO2 emissions. Additionally, we have generated more than 8 hours of employment, contributing positively to both the environment and the economy.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Toumaï Label Section -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl mb-5 md:mb-6 lg:mb-8 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
          Toumaï label by Lucie
        </h2>
        <p class="font-outfit text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-5 md:mb-6">
          With Toumaï, Lucie Agency has created a seamless labeling process, accessible to all companies trying to assess their CSR maturity. A Lucie expert makes the assessment by coming a half-day on-site. This assessment is rated on 1000 points thanks to a repository, based on the international CSR standards, the ISO 26000. We have already started the procedures and want to obtain the label before 2023.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CO2 Reduction Section -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl mb-5 md:mb-6 lg:mb-8 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
          Environmental impact
        </h2>
        <p class="font-outfit text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8 md:mb-10">
          Finally, our core business, helicopter dismantling, leads to a reduction in CO2 emissions. Indeed, thanks to our second-hand products, it's more than 14 tons of CO2 that have been saved.
        </p>
        <p class="font-outfit text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
          Saving our society and our planet, at Aviaco, we make it our mission.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20 bg-gray-900 dark:bg-black text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="font-outfit font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl mb-5 md:mb-6 lg:mb-8">
          Join us in our CSR mission
        </h2>
        <p class="font-outfit text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8 md:mb-10">
          Discover how Aviaco France is committed to creating a positive impact on society and the environment through our CSR initiatives.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <Button href="/contact" variant="secondary" size="lg" class="shadow-2xl">
            Contact us
          </Button>
          <Button href="/about" variant="outline" size="lg" class="!bg-transparent !border-2 !border-white !text-white hover:!bg-white hover:!text-gray-900 !transition-all">
            Learn more about us
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

